<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA523_07_SU_0004_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema523_su_07.css" />
  <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema523_07_0004.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_07_su_0004">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="2_pink">
        <div>
          <span lang="y">점 ㅇ을 중심으로 도형을 몇 도 돌리면 처음 도형과 완전히 겹치는지 알아봅시다.</span>
          <button type="button" class="icon_supplies" lang="y" data-supplies="pop_supplies_area_1">준비물</button>
        </div>
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="flex align_start gap_26">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">도형을 처음 도형에 완전히 겹치도록 포갠 후 점 ㅇ을 중심으로 90˚, 180˚  돌려 보세요.​</h3>
          <div class="cont_box">
            <div class="dragndrop_fraction_wrap figure_wrap">
              <div class="drag_group figure_group1">
                  <div class="drag_item figure_triangle dragpable" data-pair="1" data-value="90">
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_07_SU/0004_content.png" alt="도형 이미지" class="img">
                    <button class="btn_rotation"><span>회전버튼</span></button>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="drop_group figure_group2">
                  <div class="drop_item figure_triangle droppable drop_item1" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="90"></div>
                  <div class="drop_item figure_triangle droppable drop_item2" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="180"></div>
                  <div class="text_box">
                    <span>90˚  돌렸을 때</span>
                    <span>180˚  돌렸을 때</span>
                  </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">점 ㅇ을 중심으로 몇 도 돌렸을 때 처음 도형과 완전히 겹치는지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box mt_20 justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap flex1">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">점 ㅇ을 중심으로 180° 돌렸을 때 처음 도형과 완전히 겹칩니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_3">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize promise">
              <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>

              <div class="img_box">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_07_SU/0004_content03.png" alt="도형 이미지">
                <span lang="y" class="txt">대칭의 중심</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text_box">
                <div lang="y">
                  <span>한 도형을 어떤 점을 중심으로 180° 돌렸을 때 처음 도형과</span>
                </div>
                <div lang="y">
                  <span>완전히 겹치면 이 도형을</span>
                  <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="2">점대칭도형</button>
                  <span class="small-gap">이라고 합니다.</span>
                </div>
                <div lang="y">
                  <span>이때 그 점을</span>
                  <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="3">대칭의 중심</button>
                  <span class="small-gap">이라고 합니다. 대칭의 중심을 중심으로 180°</span>
                </div>
                <div lang="y">
                  <span>돌렸을 때 겹치는 점을</span>
                  <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="4">대응점</button>
                  <span class="small-gap">, 겹치는 변을</span>
                  <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="5">대응변</button>
                  <span class="small-gap">, 겹치는 각을</span>
                </div>
                <div lang="y">
                  <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="6">대응각</button>
                  <span class="small-gap">이라고 합니다.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true" lang="y">제출</button>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="pop_area pop_supplies_area pop_supplies_area_1">
      <div class="supplies_zoom_wrap">
        <button type="button" class="close"></button>
        <div class="supplies_zoom scrollable">
          <div class="supplies_box_wrap">
            <div class="supplies_box">
              <div class="supplies_tit">글자</div>
              <div class="supplies_contents">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_07_SU/0003_supplies.png" alt="준비물 도형 - ㄹ" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="controller">
            <button class="supplies_scale_down" disabled></button>
            <button class="supplies_scale_up"></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>